{
  "text": "The values of \u03b2 and the lattice size L were chosen to match a few of those of tables 6.2 and 6.3 of ref. [CITATION_1] . Note that the authors of ref. [CITATION_2] checked carefully for finite size effects.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "118047268",
